---
/** Vista previa de métricas (datos de ejemplo; los reales están en /app con sesión). */
---

<section
  data-landing-reveal
  style="--lr-delay: 96ms"
  class="rounded-3xl border border-violet-200/50 dark:border-violet-900/40 bg-white/55 dark:bg-gray-950/45 shadow-sm overflow-hidden"
>
  <div
    class="px-6 py-5 border-b border-gray-200/70 dark:border-gray-800/70 bg-linear-to-r from-violet-50/60 via-white/55 to-transparent dark:from-violet-950/35 dark:via-gray-950/50 dark:to-transparent backdrop-blur"
  >
    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-start justify-between gap-3">
      <div class="space-y-1 max-w-2xl">
        <p class="m-0 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide text-violet-600 dark:text-violet-300 uppercase" data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewKicker">
          Métricas
        </p>
        <h2 class="m-0 text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100" data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewTitle">
          Gráficos que cuentan tu progreso
        </h2>
        <p class="m-0 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed" data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewBody">
          En el dashboard verás barras y resúmenes con tus tecnologías reales. Aquí solo hay un ejemplo visual.
        </p>
      </div>
      <span
        class="shrink-0 rounded-full border border-amber-200/90 dark:border-amber-800/60 bg-amber-50/90 dark:bg-amber-950/40 px-2.5 py-1 text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-amber-900 dark:text-amber-200"
        data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewBadge"
      >
        Ejemplo
      </span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="p-6 space-y-4">
    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/80 dark:bg-gray-950/50 p-3">
      <div class="h-[240px] w-full" data-landing-insights-chart aria-hidden="true"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 justify-center">
      <a
        href="/app"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-violet-600 px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-violet-700 no-underline"
        data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewCtaApp"
      >
        Ver mi dashboard
      </a>
      <a
        href="/login"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 bg-white dark:bg-gray-950 px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-900 no-underline"
        data-i18n="landing.chartsPreviewCtaLogin"
      >
        Entrar
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
